sellerAgent.name: Kristina McMichael-Schwant - Kristina and Scott's MCMICHAEL TEAM

data.description:
You don't want to miss this 4 bed 2 bath one level design home. With ease of accessibility and a seamless flow between rooms. The living area is very large with several ways to make your own. 
This great home has a newer Trane HVAC  and over 2,000 sq. ft. of space.  Also included are several outbuildings one of which is a workshop. Enjoy the smaller fenced in area for kids or pets. In the winter enjoy the wood burning fireplace inside the home overlooking your property. 
Did I mention the 4+ acres?
You're outside city limits but still close to town and on all PAVED roads. 
This property is a must see to appreciate.
